1. MVP Scope
The MVP delivers a functional status engine as a pure ABAP API. A consuming application can call change_status on day one and receive a fully guarded, concurrency-safe, append-only log entry. There is no Fiori configuration app, no CDS layer, and no RAP behavior in this phase. Configuration is loaded directly into the four tables via SE16N or a test program.
